metadata.name: Migrating journey
metadata.description:
Planes are not real birds but still flying and majestic...  

This photograph has a nice story in many ways, here is why:

-This shot was taken at an operative airport from a helicopter, allowing me to fly above working planes and shoot almost what I want.

-It has been awarded in the "International B&W Spider Awards" in 2020, 5th place.

-It's an animated piece paired with a physical piece for Augmented reality use, you can print it yourself with a high-quality file provided.

The animation overlays on physical print when viewed through your phone.  
Here is the example video:  
https://youtube.com/shorts/BFZCeuyEUsc?feature=share

When I started animating this piece it gave it a second life, improved my creativity and to me, build a bridge between physical and digital art.
